25#ifndef CLEARSTATE_DEFS_H
26#define CLEARSTATE_DEFS_H
27
28enum section_id {
29 SECT_NONE,
30 SECT_CONTEXT,
31 SECT_CLEAR,
32 SECT_CTRLCONST
33};
34
35struct cs_extent_def {
36 const unsigned int *extent;
37 const unsigned int reg_index;
38 const unsigned int reg_count;
39};
40
41struct cs_section_def {
42 const struct cs_extent_def *section;
43 const enum section_id id;
44};
45
46#endif
